  "text": "Recently, ghost-free parity-violating theories of gravity have been explored in [CITATION_1] . At least in the unitary gauge in which φ is homogeneous on t = const hypersurfaces, it is found that one can indeed construct Ostrogradskystable theories. One of the theories proposed in [CITATION_2] is given by the following Lagrangian:",
